<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
    *, ::after, ::before {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
}

body.zoom{
    cursor:  url(data:image/png;base64,), auto;
}

.container{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
}

.toolbar{
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 10px;
    position: relative;
}

.toolbar input#searchByName{
    width: calc(100vw - 300px);
    padding: 1px 15px;
    border: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
    -webkit-user-select: auto;
}

.toolbar button{
    border: none;
    background-color: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.toolbar #searchBtn{
    background-color:#eee;
    padding: 2px 20px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
}

.toolbar #searchBtn svg{
    position: relative;
    top: 2px;
}

.toolbar #searchBtn:hover{
    background-color:#e6e6e6;
}

.toolbar svg.shadow{
    filter: drop-shadow( 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2));
}

.toolbar #addImages{
    background-color: #fee10b;
    border: 2px solid #eed40d;
    border-radius: 25px;
    padding: 5px 10px ;
    z-index: 0;
}

.toolbar #addImages:hover{
    background-color: #f3d911;
}

.toolbar #addImages span{
    font-weight: bold;
}

.toolbar #addImages:hover svg g{
    fill: #00813c;
}

.toolbar .search-container{
    display: inline-block;
}

.toolbar .regex{
    display: inline-block;
}

.toolbar .container-checkbox{
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 35px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 22px;
    -webkit-user-select: none;
    -moz-user-select: none;
    -ms-user-select: none;
    user-select: none;
}

.toolbar .container-checkbox input{
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    height: 0;
    width: 0;
  }

.toolbar .container-checkbox  .checkmark {
    position: absolute;
    top: -8px;
    left: 0;
    height: 25px;
    width: 25px;
    background-color: #eee;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
}

.toolbar .container-checkbox:hover input ~ .checkmark {
    background-color: #e6e6e6;
}

.toolbar .container-checkbox input:checked ~ .checkmark {
    background-color: #00813c;
    border-color: #006e34;
}

.checkmark:after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    display: none;
}

.container input:checked ~ .checkmark:after {
    display: block;
}

.container .checkmark:after {
    left: 9px;
    top: 5px;
    width: 5px;
    height: 10px;
    border: solid white;
    border-width: 0 3px 3px 0;
    -webkit-transform: rotate(45deg);
    -ms-transform: rotate(45deg);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
}

.toolbar .regex-img:hover{
    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.1);
}

.toolbar .regex-img:hover g{
    fill: #23b660;
}

.gallery{
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.highlight{
    background-color: #009646;
}

.img-container{
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 5px;
    width: 200px;
    background-color: #fff;

    position: relative;
}

.img-container .zoom-image{
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    cursor: pointer;
    transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
}

.loader-container,
.loaded-container{
    display: inline-block;
    height: 200px;
    width: 200px;
    position: relative;
}

.loader-container .image-loader,
.loader-container .image-error{
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

.img-container  .image{
    width: 190px;
    height: 190px;
    object-fit: cover;
    text-align: center;
}

.img-container  .loaded-container.selectImage{
    opacity: 0.8;
    transform: scale(0.9);
    background-color: #009646;
    border-color: #009646;
}

.img-container  div.loader-container.selectImage{
    transform: scale(0.9);
    border: 5px solid #32aa6a;
}

.img-container .img-text{
    padding: 4px;
}

.img-thumbnail {
	padding: .25rem;
	background-color: #fff;
	border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
	border-radius: .25rem;
    max-width: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-out,
        opacity 0.2s ease-out;
}

div.zoom{
    transform: scale(1.15)!important;
    opacity: 1!important;
    z-index: 999;
}

div.zoom svg{
    filter: drop-shadow( 1px 1px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .5));
}

.pagination {
    display: inline-block;
    width: max-content;
    margin: 0 auto;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%,0);
}

.pagination a {
    color: black;
    float: left;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
    background-color: #fff;
}

.pagination a.active {
    background-color: #009646;
    color: white;
    border: 1px solid #009646;
}

.pagination a:hover:not(.active) {background-color: #dee2e6;}

.pagination a#input{
    border: none;
}

.pagination a:first-child {
    border-top-left-radius: 5px;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
    border-right: none;
}

.pagination a:last-child {
    border-top-right-radius: 5px;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
    border-left: none;
}

.pagination a#input input{
    border: none;
    width: 30px;
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #009646;
    height: 18.5px;
    -webkit-user-select: auto;
}

.pagination a#input span{
    height: 18.5px;
    display: inline-block;
}

.pagination a#input:hover{
    background: transparent;
}

.zoomImage-container{
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.75);
    z-index: 9999999;
}

.zoomImage{
    display: inline-block;
}

.zoomImage .image{
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 98vh;
}

.closeButton{
    position: absolute;
    right: 5px;
    top: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.counter{
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 10px;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mark.js/8.11.1/mark.min.js" integrity="sha256-IdYuEFP3WJ/mNlzM18Y20Xgav3h5pgXYzl8fW4GnuPo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script>
    var call1C = null;
    let listerens =  [];

let gallery = {
    imageWidth: 210,
    imageHeight: 210,
    
    galleryDivWidth: 0,
    
    imagesAmount: 0,
    imagesAmountByX: 0,
    imagesAmountByY: 0,
    maxImageContainerHeight: 0,
    
    imagesArray: [],
    filteredArray: [],
    selectedImages: 0,
    

    calcPicturesAmountInWidth() {
        const innerWidth = window.innerWidth;
        if(innerWidth <= 0) {
            throw new InputError("Invalid input value: " + currentWidth);
        };

        this.imagesAmountByX = Math.floor(innerWidth / this.imageWidth);
        this.imagesAmountByX < 1 ? this.imagesAmountByX = 1 : '';
        return this.imagesAmountByX;
    },

    calculateGalleryNewWidth(){
        if(this.imagesAmountByX <= 0){
            throw new InputError('Input value couldn`t be 0 or less.');
        }
        
        this.galleryDivWidth  = this.imagesAmountByX * this.imageWidth;
        return this.galleryDivWidth;
    },

    resizeGalleryWidth() {
        this.calcPicturesAmountInWidth();
        const newWidth = this.calculateGalleryNewWidth();
        UI.changeGalleryWidth(newWidth);
    },

    calcImgMaxHeight() {
        let imgsArray = Array.prototype.slice.call(UI.galleryDiv.children);
        this.maxImageContainerHeight = Math.max(...imgsArray.map( element => element.children[1].clientHeight + this.imageHeight));
        this.maxImageContainerHeight < this.imageHeight ? this.maxImageContainerHeight = this.imageHeight : '';
    },

    calculateImageAmountInHeight() {
        if (!this.maxImageContainerHeight) return;
        const innerHeight= window.innerHeight;
        this.imagesAmountByY = Math.floor((innerHeight - UI.toolbarHeight - UI.pagination.clientHeight) / this.maxImageContainerHeight);
        this.imagesAmountByY  < 1 ? this.imagesAmountByY  = 1 : '';
        return this.imagesAmountByY ;
    },

    addSelectedFieldInImageObject(selectedImagesArray){
        selectedImagesArray.forEach(selectedImage => {
            const selectedID = selectedImage.ID;
            const imageIndex = this.imagesArray.findIndex(img => img.ID === selectedID);
            imageIndex > -1 ? this.imagesArray[imageIndex].Selected = true : '';
            gallery.selectedImages++;
            UI.changeAddSelectedImagesBtn();
        })
    }
}

let paginationObj = {
    currentPage: 1,
    imgPerPage: 1,
    pagesAmount: 1,

    calculateImagesPerPage() {
        let imagesPerPage = gallery.imagesAmountByX * gallery.imagesAmountByY;
        return imagesPerPage;
    },

    calculatePagesAmount() {
        if(!this.imgPerPage || !gallery.imagesAmount) {
            this.pagesAmount = 1;
            return;
        }
        this.pagesAmount = Math.ceil(gallery.imagesAmount / this.imgPerPage);
    },

    changePage(page) {
        if(page <= 0) this.currentPage = page = 1;
        if (page > this.pagesAmount) this.currentPage = page = this.pagesAmount;
        if(gallery.imagesAmount === 0 && !toolbarObj.filterValue) return false;
    
        let idsForImagesWithoutSrc = [];
        
        let displayImages = [];
        for (let i = (page - 1) * this.imgPerPage; i < (page * this.imgPerPage); i++) {
            const targetImage = gallery.filteredArray.length !== 0 ?  gallery.filteredArray[i] : toolbarObj.filterValue ? gallery.filteredArray[i] : gallery.imagesArray[i];
            if(targetImage) {
                displayImages.push(targetImage);
                if(!targetImage.Preview){
                    idsForImagesWithoutSrc.push(targetImage.ID);
                }
            };
        }
    
        UI.addImagesInGallery(displayImages);
        UI.pagination.querySelector('#currentPage').value = page;
        if(idsForImagesWithoutSrc.length !== 0)  send_to_1C('call1C', `{"value":"get_images_src", "ids":"${idsForImagesWithoutSrc}"}`);
    }
}

let toolbarObj = {
    searchByRegexp: false,
    filterValue: '',

    markResult(tdElement){
        let instance = new Mark(tdElement);
        instance.unmark();
        instance[toolbarObj.searchByRegexp ? 'markRegExp' : 'mark'](toolbarObj.filterValue,  {
          "element": "span",
          "className": "highlight"
        });
    },

    setNewFilteredArray(filter){
        filter = filter.toLowerCase();
        const filtersArray = filter.trim().split(' ').filter(f => f);
        toolbarObj.filterValue = filtersArray;
    
        gallery.imagesArray.forEach(image => {
            if(filtersArray.every(filter => image.Name.toLowerCase().indexOf(filter) > -1)){
                gallery.filteredArray.push(image);
            }
        })
    },

    setNewFilteredArrayRegExp(filter){
        const filterRegExp = new RegExp(filter, 'i');
        this.filterValue = filterRegExp;

        gallery.imagesArray.forEach(image => {
            if(filterRegExp.test(image.Name)){
                gallery.filteredArray.push(image);
            }
        })
    }
}

let UI = {
    galleryDiv: document.querySelector('#gallery'),
    toolbar: document.querySelector('#toolbar'),
    pagination: document.querySelector('#pagination'),
    toolbarHeight: 50,

    
    changeGalleryWidth(newWidth){
        if(newWidth <= 0){
            throw new InputError('Input value couldn`t be 0 or less.');
        }
    
        if(typeof(newWidth) !== 'number'){
            throw new InputError('Incorrect type of input value ('+typeof(newWidth)+'). Should be a number.');
        }
    
        this.galleryDiv.style.width = newWidth + 'px';
    },

    changeAddSelectedImagesBtn() {
        this.toolbar.querySelector('#addImages span').innerHTML = `Add <span style="color: green;">${gallery.selectedImages ? gallery.selectedImages : ''}</span> Selected Images`;
        this.toolbar.querySelector('input').style.width = `calc(100vw - ${(this.toolbar.querySelector('#addImages').clientWidth + this.toolbar.querySelector('#regexSearch').clientWidth + this.toolbar.querySelector('#searchBtn').clientWidth + 50)}px)`
    },

    changePagesAmountInPagination() {
        if(!paginationObj.pagesAmount || paginationObj.pagesAmount < 0) paginationObj.pagesAmount = 1;
        this.pagination.querySelector('#pagesAmount').innerText = '/'+ paginationObj.pagesAmount;
        this.pagination.querySelector('#currentPage').style.width = paginationObj.pagesAmount.toString().length * 10 + 'px';
    },

    waitUntiImareSrcLoading(image, loadingSrc, callback) {
        let downloadingImage = new Image();

        downloadingImage.onload = function(){
            if(!document.body.contains(image)) return;
            image.src = this.src;
            callback !== undefined ? callback() : '';
        };

        downloadingImage.onerror = function(){
            if(!document.body.contains(image)) return;
            image.src = errorImageSrc;
            if(image.classList.contains('image-loader')){
                image.classList.remove('image-loader');
                image.classList.add('image-error');
            }
        };

        downloadingImage.src = loadingSrc;
    },

    selectedImageInGallery(imageContainer) {
        const imgID = imageContainer.children[0].getAttribute('data-id');
        const targetImageIndex = gallery.imagesArray.findIndex(img => img.ID === imgID);
        if(targetImageIndex < 0) return;
        if(imageContainer.classList.contains('selectImage')){
            imageContainer.classList.remove('selectImage');
            gallery.selectedImages -= 1;
            gallery.imagesArray[targetImageIndex].Selected = false;
        }else{
            imageContainer.classList.add('selectImage');
            gallery.selectedImages += 1;
            gallery.imagesArray[targetImageIndex].Selected = true;
        }
     
        this.changeAddSelectedImagesBtn();
    },

    addImagesInGallery(images){
        if(!images.length && !toolbarObj.filterValue) return false;
        this.galleryDiv.innerHTML = '';
        images.forEach(img => {
            // const imageSrc = img.Src ? img.Src : img.Preview ? img.Preview : '';
            let divContainer = document.createElement('div');
            divContainer.className = 'img-container filtered loaded';
            divContainer.innerHTML = `
                <div class="img-thumbnail loader-container ${typeof(img.Selected) !== 'undefined' && img.Selected ? 'selectImage' : ''}">
                <img src='${loaderImageScr}'
                class="image-loader" data-id="${img.ID}"></div>
                <div class="img-text">${img.Name !== undefined ? img.Name : ''}</div>
            `;
            this.galleryDiv.appendChild(divContainer);

            if(img.Preview){
                let image = divContainer.querySelector('img');
                UI.waitUntiImareSrcLoading(image, img.Preview, () => {
                    image.className = 'image';
                    image.parentNode.className = image.parentNode.className.replace('loader-container', 'loaded-container');
                });
            }

            if(toolbarObj.filterValue){
                const textNode = divContainer.querySelector('.img-text');
                toolbarObj.markResult(textNode);
            }
        });

        this.galleryDiv.querySelectorAll('.img-thumbnail').forEach(img => {
            img.children[0].addEventListener('click', imageSelect);
            img.addEventListener('mouseenter', onImageEnter);
            img.addEventListener('mouseleave', onImageLeave);
        });
    },

    imageEnterDisplay(img){
        img.parentNode.classList.add('zoom');
        let zoomButton = document.createElement('div');
        zoomButton.classList.add('zoom-image');
        zoomButton.innerHTML = `
        <svg x="0px" y="0px"
            width="40" height="40"
            viewBox="0 0 172 172"
            style=" fill:#000000;">
            <g fill="none" fill-rule="nonzero" stroke="none" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="butt" stroke-linejoin="miter" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-dasharray="" stroke-dashoffset="0" font-family="none" font-weight="none" font-size="none" text-anchor="none" style="mix-blend-mode: normal"><path d="M0,172v-172h172v172z" fill="none">
            </path>
            <g fill="#ffffff"><path d="M64.5,14.33333c-27.6214,0 -50.16667,22.54527 -50.16667,50.16667c0,27.6214 22.54527,50.16667 50.16667,50.16667c12.52732,0 23.97256,-4.67249 32.7819,-12.31771l3.05143,3.05143v9.26628l43,43l14.33333,-14.33333l-43,-43h-9.26628l-3.05143,-3.05143c7.64521,-8.80934 12.31771,-20.25458 12.31771,-32.7819c0,-27.6214 -22.54527,-50.16667 -50.16667,-50.16667zM64.5,28.66667c19.87509,0 35.83333,15.95824 35.83333,35.83333c0,19.87509 -15.95825,35.83333 -35.83333,35.83333c-19.87509,0 -35.83333,-15.95825 -35.83333,-35.83333c0,-19.87509 15.95824,-35.83333 35.83333,-35.83333zM57.33333,43v14.33333h-14.33333v14.33333h14.33333v14.33333h14.33333v-14.33333h14.33333v-14.33333h-14.33333v-14.33333z"></path></g></g>
        </svg>`;
        img.parentNode.appendChild(zoomButton);
        zoomButton.addEventListener('click', zoomImage);
    },

    imageLeaveDisplay(img){
        img.parentNode.classList.remove('zoom');
        img.nextElementSibling !== null ? img.nextElementSibling.remove() : '';
    },

    addZoomImage(image){
        image.src = loaderImageScr;

        let imageZoomContainer = document.createElement('div');
        imageZoomContainer.classList.add('zoomImage-container');
        let imageContainer = document.createElement('div');
        imageContainer.classList.add('zoomImage');
        imageContainer.appendChild(image);
        imageZoomContainer.appendChild(imageContainer);
        imageZoomContainer.innerHTML += `<div class="closeButton" id="closeZoomImage">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" x="0px" y="0px"
            width="30" height="30"
            viewBox="0 0 172 172"
            style=" fill:#000000;"><g fill="none" fill-rule="nonzero" stroke="none" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="butt" stroke-linejoin="miter" stroke-miterlimit="10" stroke-dasharray="" stroke-dashoffset="0" font-family="none" font-weight="none" font-size="none" text-anchor="none" style="mix-blend-mode: normal"><path d="M0,172v-172h172v172z" fill="none"></path><g fill="#ffffff"><path d="M136.16667,21.5h-100.33333c-7.91917,0 -14.33333,6.41417 -14.33333,14.33333v100.33333c0,7.91917 6.41417,14.33333 14.33333,14.33333h100.33333c7.91917,0 14.33333,-6.41417 14.33333,-14.33333v-100.33333c0,-7.91917 -6.41417,-14.33333 -14.33333,-14.33333zM121.83333,111.72833l-10.105,10.105l-25.72833,-25.72833l-25.72833,25.72833l-10.105,-10.105l25.72833,-25.72833l-25.72833,-25.72833l10.105,-10.105l25.72833,25.72833l25.72833,-25.72833l10.105,10.105l-25.72833,25.72833z"></path></g></g></svg>
        </div>`;
        document.body.querySelector('.container').appendChild(imageZoomContainer);

        //events
        imageZoomContainer.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
            if(e.target === this) this.remove();
        });
        imageZoomContainer.querySelector('#closeZoomImage').addEventListener('click', function(){this.parentNode.remove();})

        const nodeImage = imageZoomContainer.querySelector('img');
        const imageId = image.getAttribute('data-id');
        const targetImage = gallery.imagesArray.find(img => img.ID === imageId);
        const imageSrc = targetImage.Src;
        imageSrc ? UI.waitUntiImareSrcLoading(nodeImage, imageSrc) : send_to_1C('call1C', `{"value":"zoom_image", "id":"${imageId}"}`);

    },

    resizeGallery() {
        gallery.calcPicturesAmountInWidth();
        gallery.calculateImageAmountInHeight();
        const newImgsPerPage = paginationObj.calculateImagesPerPage();
        if(pagination.imgPerPage !== newImgsPerPage) {
            paginationObj.imgPerPage = newImgsPerPage;
            paginationObj.calculatePagesAmount();
            this.changePagesAmountInPagination();
            paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage);
            gallery.resizeGalleryWidth();
        }
    },

    fillOtherDataForGallery(){
        gallery.resizeGalleryWidth();
        gallery.calcImgMaxHeight();
        gallery.calculateImageAmountInHeight();
        paginationObj.imgPerPage = paginationObj.calculateImagesPerPage();
        paginationObj.calculatePagesAmount();
        this.changePagesAmountInPagination();
        paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage = 1);
        addEventListenersForPagination();
        addEventListenersForToolbar();
    }
}

let loaderImageScr = `data:image/gif;base64,`;
let errorImageSrc = `data:image/png;base64,`;
class InputError extends Error{};

////////////called from 1C/////////////

function fillImagesSrc(jsonData){
    const data = JSON.parse(jsonData);
    const imagesDataArray = data.Pictures;

    imagesDataArray.forEach(img => {
        const imageNode = UI.galleryDiv.querySelector('[data-id="'+img.ID+'"]');
        gallery.imagesArray.find(image => image.ID === img.ID).Preview = img.Preview;

        if(imageNode === null) return;

        UI.waitUntiImareSrcLoading(imageNode, img.Preview, () => {
            imageNode.className = 'image';
            imageNode.parentNode.className = imageNode.parentNode.className.replace('loader-container', 'loaded-container');
        })
    })
}

function fillImageZoomSrc(jsonData){
    const data = JSON.parse(jsonData);
    const imagesDataArray = data.Pictures;

    imagesDataArray.forEach(img => {
        const zoomImage = document.querySelector('.zoomImage .image');
        gallery.imagesArray.find(image => image.ID === img.ID).Src = img.Src;

        if(zoomImage === null) return;
        UI.waitUntiImareSrcLoading(zoomImage, img.Src);
    })
}

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////


//////event functions
function imageSelect() {
    let imageContainer = this.parentNode;
    UI.selectedImageInGallery(imageContainer);
}

function zoomImage() {
    let image = this.previousElementSibling.cloneNode(true);
    if(image.classList.contains('image-loader')) return;
    UI.addZoomImage(image);
}

const onImageEnter = (e) => {
    const img = e.target.children[0];
    UI.imageEnterDisplay(img);
}

const onImageLeave = (e) => {
    const img = e.target.children[0];
    UI.imageLeaveDisplay(img);
}

// event functions
function searchInGallery(){
    let filter = this.value;
    gallery.filteredArray = [];

    toolbarObj.searchByRegexp ? toolbarObj.setNewFilteredArrayRegExp(filter) : toolbarObj.setNewFilteredArray(filter);

    gallery.filteredArray.length !== 0 ? gallery.imagesAmount =  gallery.filteredArray.length : toolbarObj.filterValue ? gallery.imagesAmount = 0 : '';
    paginationObj.calculatePagesAmount();
    UI.changePagesAmountInPagination();
    paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage);
    gallery.resizeGalleryWidth();
}

//send data to 1C
function send_to_1C(name, data){ 
	call1C = data;
	call1CEvent.click();
    //var event = new MouseEvent('click', {
    //  'view': window,
    //  'bubbles': true,
    //  'cancelable': true
    //});
    //event.propertyName = name;
    //event.data = data; 
    //document.dispatchEvent(event);
}

function changeSearchMethod(){
    const checked = this.checked;
    toolbarObj.searchByRegexp = checked;
    if(!toolbarObj.filterValue) return;
    const searchInput = UI.toolbar.querySelector('#searchByName');
    searchInGallery.call(searchInput);
}

//add to events UI
const addEventListenersForPagination = () => {
    if(listerens.indexOf('pagination') > -1) return;

    UI.pagination.querySelector('#firstPage').addEventListener('click', () =>{
        if(paginationObj.currentPage === 1) return;
        paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage = 1);
    });

    UI.pagination.querySelector('#lastPage').addEventListener('click', () => {
        if(paginationObj.currentPage === paginationObj.pagesAmount) return;
        paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage = paginationObj.pagesAmount);
    });

    UI.pagination.querySelector('#previousPage').addEventListener('click', () => {
        if(paginationObj.currentPage === 1) return;
        paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage -= 1);
    });

    UI.pagination.querySelector('#nextPage').addEventListener('click', () => {
        if(paginationObj.currentPage === paginationObj.pagesAmount) return;
        paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage += 1);
    });

    UI.pagination.querySelector('a#input').addEventListener('click', function () {
        const inputArea = this.children[0];
        inputArea.focus();
    })

    UI.pagination.querySelector('#currentPage').addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
        if(e.keyCode !== 13) return;
        let enterPage = +this.value;
        typeof(enterPage) !== 'number' || enterPage <= 0 || !enterPage ? enterPage = 1 : '';
        paginationObj.changePage(paginationObj.currentPage = enterPage);
    })

    listerens.push('pagination');
}

const addEventListenersForToolbar = () => {
    if(listerens.indexOf('toolbar') > -1) return;
    const searchInput = UI.toolbar.querySelector('#searchByName');

    UI.toolbar.querySelector('#addImages').addEventListener('click', () => {
        if(!gallery.selectedImages) return false;
        const ids =  gallery.imagesArray.filter(img => typeof(img.Selected) !== 'undefined' && img.Selected).map(img => img.ID);
        send_to_1C('call1C', `{"value":"selected_images", "ids":"${ids}"}`);
    })
    searchInput.value = '';
    searchInput.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
        if(e.keyCode !== 13) return;
        searchInGallery.call(e.target);
    });
    UI.toolbar.querySelector('#searchBtn').addEventListener('click', function() {
        searchInGallery.call(searchInput);
    });
    UI.toolbar.querySelector('#regexSearch input').addEventListener('change', changeSearchMethod);
    toolbarObj.searchByRegexp = UI.toolbar.querySelector('#regexSearch input').checked;
}

function fillImageGallery(jsonData) {
    if(!jsonData) return;
    const data = JSON.parse(jsonData);
    const images = data.Pictures !== undefined ? data.Pictures : [];
    const selectedImages = data.Selected !== undefined ? data.Selected : [];

    gallery.imagesAmount = images.length;
    if(!gallery.imagesAmount) return false;

    const imagesWithNewData = images.slice(0, images.length);
    imagesWithNewData.forEach(img => {
        const imagePreview = img.Preview ? img.Preview : img.Src ? img.Src : '';
        const imageSrc = img.Src ? img.Src : img.Preview ? img.Preview : '';
        img.Preview = imagePreview;
        img.Src = imageSrc;
    });
    gallery.imagesArray = imagesWithNewData;

    selectedImages.length !== 0 ? gallery.addSelectedFieldInImageObject(selectedImages) : '';
    //       
    UI.addImagesInGallery(gallery.imagesArray.slice(0,100));
    UI.fillOtherDataForGallery();

    window.addEventListener('resize', () =>{UI.resizeGallery()});
}
    </script>
    <button id="call1CEvent" style="display: none">call1C</button>
